Serialized Fields

suppressedExceptions

java.util.List<E> suppressedExceptions
The list of suppressed exceptions, as returned by ImportException.getSuppressedBackport(). The list is initialized to a zero-element unmodifiable sentinel list. When a serialized Throwable is read in, if the suppressedExceptions field points to a zero-element list, the field is reset to the sentinel value.
